- **Text first** (modern VLMs): `Idefics3Processor._call(text, images)`, `Qwen2VLProcessor._call(text, images)`, `SmolVLMProcessor` (= Idefics3Processor)
- **Images first** (older VLMs): `LlavaProcessor._call(images, text)`, `PaliGemmaProcessor._call(images, text)`, `Florence2Processor._call(images, text)`

The pipeline will use the **text-first** convention: `this.processor(text, preparedImages)`, matching the majority of current modern VLMs and the Python transformers convention.

